\"\">支持将 Markdown 内容转换为 HTML 和 PDF 格式</span>\n     </section></li>\n    <li>\n     <section style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;line-height:1.5em;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\">\n      <span leaf=\"\">提供实时预览和快速编译速度</span>\n     </section></li>\n    <li>\n     <section style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;line-height:1.5em;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\">\n      <span leaf=\"\">允许用户定义自定义函数和变量，增强灵活性</span>\n     </section></li>\n    <li>\n     <section style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;line-height:1.5em;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\">\n      <span leaf=\"\">包含丰富的标准库，支持布局构建、输入输出、数学运算等功能</span>\n     </section></li>\n    <li>\n     <section style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;line-height:1.5em;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\">\n      <span leaf=\"\">兼容 CommonMark 及 GFM，并引入多种语法扩展</span>\n     </section></li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding-top: 0px;padding-bottom: 0px;padding-left: 10px;padding-right: 0px;display: block;color: rgb(0, 150, 136);margin-top: 0.2rem;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom: 0.2rem;margin-left: auto;border-left-width: 3px;border-left-style: solid;border-left-color: rgb(0, 150, 136);\"><span style=\"display: none;\"></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0em;display:block;font-size:22px;line-height:1.5em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">coinbase/agentkit</span><span style=\"font-size: 0.58em;font-weight: normal;font-style: italic;color: graytext;display: block;text-decoration: underline;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span leaf=\"\">https://github.com/coinbase/agentkit</span></span></span><span style=\"display: none;\"></span></h2>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding-top:3px;letter-spacing:0em;padding-left:0px;font-size:16px;padding-bottom:3px;line-heig