px;\"><span leaf=\"\">AgentKit 是 Coinbase 开发平台的框架，旨在轻松使 AI 代理能够在链上执行操作。该项目设计为与任何 AI 框架和钱包兼容。</span></p>\n   <ul style=\"margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;list-style-type:disc;padding-left:1rem;padding-bottom:0px;margin-top:8px;margin-bottom:8px;margin-right:0px;padding-right:0px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li>\n     <section style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;line-height:1.5em;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\">\n      <span leaf=\"\">支持 Node.js 和 Python 两种语言</span>\n     </section></li>\n    <li>\n     <section style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;line-height:1.5em;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\">\n      <span leaf=\"\">提供简单的快速启动指南</span>\n     </section></li>\n    <li>\n     <section style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;line-height:1.5em;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\">\n      <span leaf=\"\">可与多种钱包和 AI 框架集成</span>\n     </section></li>\n    <li>\n     <section style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;line-height:1.5em;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\">\n      <span leaf=\"\">组织为单一代码库，包含多个示例和扩展包</span>\n     </section></li>\n    <li>\n     <section style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;line-height:1.5em;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\">\n      <span leaf=\"\">实现了通过聊天模式直接进行链上操作</span>\n     </section></li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding-top: 0px;padding-bottom: 0px;padding-left: 10px;padding-right: 0px;display: block;color: rgb(0, 150, 136);margin-top: 0.2rem;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom: 0.2rem;margin-left: auto;border-left-width: 3px;border-left-style: solid;border-left-color: rgb(0, 150, 136);\"><span style=\"display: none;\"></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0em;display:block;font-size:22px;line-height:1.5em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">HITsz-TMG/UMOE-Scaling-Unified-Multimodal-LLMs</span><